Class Obstacle

java.lang.Object
tr.edu.ku.devnull.needforspear.Model.Obstacle.Obstacle
Direct Known Subclasses:
ExplosiveObstacle, FirmObstacle, GiftObstacle, HollowPurpleObstacle, SimpleObstacle
public class Obstacle
extends java.lang.Object
Obstacle is a class that extends ObstacleDescription which contains information regarding an obstacle's attributes.
